{
  "texts": [
    "The test set contains 20% of labeled LUNA16.",
    "We divided the data into test, train, and validation sets based on nodule ID.Data that we eliminated due to inadequate annotation are considered unlabeled data in semi-supervised learning.",
    "We continue the training until the model labels most of the data with more than 90% confidence.",
    "Validation and test sets are fixed in these trainings.",
    "Next, we try various intensity range filters on 3D data in multiple ways, to analyze the effect of model performance on different parameter setting which is shown in Fig. 4."
  ]
}